  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Executive",
  "description": "<p>The Business Development Executive helps expand Company’s distribution network, partnerships, and retail channels across Singapore, Malaysia, Vietnam, and regional markets. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>This role drives growth for Company’s ecosystem—including products, solutions, and international trade partnerships.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><u>Sales &amp; Partnerships</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and secure new B2B partners: convenience stores, supermarkets, cafés, hotels, attractions, retailers, distributors, and export partners</li>\n  <li>Pitch Company’s brands and products to corporate partners</li>\n  <li>Negotiate pricing, trading terms, and supply agreements</li>\n  <li>Support onboarding of new merchants for company machines/programs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Account Management</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain relationships with existing partners and distributors</li>\n  <li>Ensure product availability, merchandising, and promotion execution</li>\n  <li>Track sales performance and prepare weekly/monthly reports</li>\n  <li>Channel Expansion</li>\n  <li>Grow presence in SG/MY/VN convenience channels (7-Eleven, FamilyMart, GS25, CU)</li>\n  <li>Support entry into new export markets </li>\n  <li>Identify strategic collaborations with malls, landlords, and lifestyle partners</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Project Support</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in organizing sampling events, roadshows, exhibitions, and partnerships</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with supply chain, marketing, and finance teams for smooth operations</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/Degree in Business, Marketing, or related field</li>\n  <li>1–3 years of sales or BD experience (FMCG, retail, F&amp;B preferred)</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and negotiation skills</li>\n  <li>Self-driven, proactive, and able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel when required</li>\n</ul>",
